{"tid":2246512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己有柒頭恐懼症","createTime":"2020-10-17T06:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T07:38:02.000Z","uid":349136,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a43851b3af869d35261e86a9b79def8463bd2456","tid":2246512,"uid":349136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"每次喺街見到啲柒頭都好想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解佢地咁柒都有勇氣出街<br />\n唔覺得自己影響市容嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前返學有個女同學真係好柒<br />\n又肥 小剛眼 成龍鼻 成隻豬咁<br />\n個頭笠到可以煎蛋食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次同fd 挑戰望佢60秒<br />\n30秒都未夠就嘔咗出嚟<br />\n條女唔知仲問我有冇事 係唔係唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b95164e446201dd6af8810dffa902b553c51b2","tid":2246512,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:47:00.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉 洗唔洗咁樣迫害我地柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2400ad52af741d30f65202d4aa1aac1859f9ab1","tid":2246512,"uid":349136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4b95164e446201dd6af8810dffa902b553c51b2","tid":2246512,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:47:00.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉 洗唔洗咁樣迫害我地柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"不如你地戴一世口罩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a65cdf274844b178183e047f4c5a4daa310905","tid":2246512,"uid":221430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2400ad52af741d30f65202d4aa1aac1859f9ab1","tid":2246512,"uid":349136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4b95164e446201dd6af8810dffa902b553c51b2","tid":2246512,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:47:00.0